{"url":"https://www.heiwa-net.co.jp/recruit/career/office-tour.html","html":"\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang='ja'>\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n  <meta charset='UTF-8'>\r\n<meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge'>\r\n<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'>\r\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\r\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\r\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Abel&family=Crimson+Text:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@100..900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&family=Roboto+Mono:ital,wght@0,100..700;1,100..700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n<link rel='stylesheet' href='assets/css/style.css'>\r\n<script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"assets/js/common.js\"></script>\r\n  <title>オフィスツアー｜平和不動産株式会社</title>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n  <header class='l-header isReverse'>\r\n  \r\n  <a href='index.html' class=\"l-header_logo\">\r\n    <img src='assets/img/common/logo_w.png' alt='平和不動産　MID-CAREER RECRUITING' class=\"l-header_logo_w\">\r\n    <img src='assets/img/common/logo_color.png' alt='' class=\"l-header_logo_color\">\r\n  </a>\r\n  \r\n  <a href='' class='l-header_menubar u-sp js-menubar'><span></span><span></span><span></span></a>\r\n  <nav class='l-header_links js-menu'>\r\n    <a href='index.html' class='l-header_links_link '>TOP</a>\r\n    <a href='index.html#interview' class='l-header_links_link '>INTERVIEW</a>\r\n    <a href='index.html#business' class='l-header_links_link '>BUSINESS</a>\r\n    <a href='benefit.html' class='l-header_links_link '>ENVIRONMENT</a>\r\n    <a href='message.html' class='l-header_links_link '>MESSAGE</a>\r\n    <a href='requirement.html' class='l-header_links_rq'>募集要項</a>\r\n  </nav>\r\n</header>\r\n  \r\n<section id=\"office-tour-header\">\r\n    <div class=\"bg\">\r\n        <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-head-01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\r\n        <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-head-02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\r\n        <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-head-03.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"page-header-cnt\">\r\n        <h2>オフィスツアー</h2>\r\n        <p class=\"desc\">平和不動産では、働きやすい職場環境づくりを推進しています。<br>本店社員が働いている日証館のオフィスを紹介します。</p>\r\n        <h1 class=\"cursive large\">Office Tour</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section id=\"office-tour\">\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block entrance fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-entrance-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">01</span>\r\n                        <p>ようこそ、平和不動産へ！</p>\r\n                        <h3>エントランス</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>当社が本店を置く日証館は、旧渋沢栄一邸の跡地に昭和3年（1928年）に建設され、証券業界の歴史を担ってきました。<br>優れた外観意匠で、証券会社が立ち並んだ日本橋兜町の雰囲気を今に伝える建物です。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-entrance-01.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-entrance-02.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block lounge-01 fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-01-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">02</span>\r\n                        <p>打ち合わせにも休憩にも</p>\r\n                        <h3>ラウンジ</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>お洒落なラウンジは社内コミュニケーションの場。<br>ラウンジにいれば自然と人が集まります。<br>グリーンも多く配置されており、リラックスにも最適です。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-01.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-02.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-03.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-04.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block lounge-02 fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">03</span>\r\n                        <p>気軽にコーヒーブレイク</p>\r\n                        <h3>福利厚生サービス</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>ラウンジにはコーヒーサーバーを設置。<br>コーヒーだけでなくカフェラテやココアも選べます。<br>大人気の社食サービスは売り切れ必至です。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-05.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-06.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block lounge-03 fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-03-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">04</span>\r\n                        <p>どこでも仕事できます</p>\r\n                        <h3>充実の設備</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>持ち運び可能な充電バッテリーを10台準備。<br>ノートPCにも打ち合わせモニターにも利用可能です。<br>ここで仕事をすれば新しいアイデアが生まれるかも。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-07.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-08.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-lounge-09.jpg\" alt=\"Lounge\"></figure>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block space fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-space-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">05</span>\r\n                        <p>話かけないで！</p>\r\n                        <h3>集中ブース</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>一人で仕事に集中したいときはココ。<br>原則会話は禁止です。<br>マルチディスプレイや昇降可能なデスクを導入しています。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-space-01.jpg\" alt=\"集中ブース\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-space-02.jpg\" alt=\"集中ブース\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-space-03.jpg\" alt=\"集中ブース\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-space-04.jpg\" alt=\"集中ブース\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-space-05.jpg\" alt=\"集中ブース\"></figure>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block room fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-room-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">06</span>\r\n                        <p>役員会議室はいつも緊張します</p>\r\n                        <h3>会議室・応接室</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>社内外の打合せ等で利用できる会議室を大小設置。<br>重厚感のある役員会議室は言葉のとおり役員会議で利用されます。<br>滅多に入れない応接室は役員優先です。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-room-01.jpg\" alt=\"会議室​\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-room-02.jpg\" alt=\"会議室​\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-room-03.jpg\" alt=\"会議室​\"></figure>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n    <div class=\"office-tour-block restroom fadein\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/officetour/office-tour-restroom-bg.jpg);\">\r\n        <div class=\"office-tour-cnt\">\r\n            <div class=\"office-tour-block-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"desc sans-serif\">\r\n                    <div class=\"blocktitle\">\r\n                        <span class=\"num\">07</span>\r\n                        <p>ちょっと一休み</p>\r\n                        <h3>休養室​</h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>ソファや簡易ベッドを備えた休養室は男女別で設置。<br>集中力が切れたときは思い切って一休み。<br>いつでも気軽に利用できます。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-restroom-01.jpg\" alt=\"休養室​\"></figure>\r\n                <figure><img src=\"assets/img/officetour/office-tour-restroom-02.jpg\" alt=\"休養室​\"></figure>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- office-tour-block -->\r\n</section>\r\n  <a href='#' class='l-anchor'>PAGE TOP</a>\r\n  <nav class='l-localnav'>\r\n  <a href='https://www.heiwa-net.co.jp/corporate/about.html' class='l-localnav_link -ext' target=\"_blank\">会社概要</a>\r\n  <a href='https://www.heiwa-net.co.jp/corporate/history.html' class='l-localnav_link -ext' target=\"_blank\">沿革</a>\r\n  <a href='message.html' class='l-localnav_link -int'>メッセージ</a>\r\n  <a href='requirement.html' class='l-localnav_link -int'>募集要項</a>\r\n</nav>\r\n  <footer class='l-footer'>\r\n  <address class='l-footer_meta'>\r\n    <a href='index.html' class='l-footer_meta_logo'><img src='assets/img/common/logo_w.png' alt='平和不動産 MID-CAREER RECRUITINNG'></a>\r\n    <small class='l-footer_meta_copyright'>Copyright &copy; HEIWA REAL ESTATE CO., LTD. All rights reserved.</small>\r\n  </address>\r\n  <nav class='l-footer_links'>\r\n    <a href='index.html' class='l-footer_links_link'>TOP</a>\r\n    <a href='index.html#interview' class='l-footer_links_link'>INTERVIEW</a>\r\n    <a href='index.html#business' class='l-footer_links_link'>BUSINESS</a>\r\n    <a href='benefit.html' class='l-footer_links_link'>ENVIRONMENT</a>\r\n    <a href='message.html' class='l-footer_links_link'>MESSAGE</a>\r\n    <a href='https://www.heiwa-net.co.jp/' class='l-footer_links_ext' target=\"_blank\">コーポレートサイト</a>\r\n  </nav>\r\n</footer>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.heiwa-net.co.jp/recruit/career/office-tour.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T18:54:13.308Z"}